lead_paragraph: Duan Yingying overcame Misa Eguchi of Japan 6-4, 7-6 (7) at the Jiangxi Open semifinals on Saturday to set up a title match against sixth-seeded Vania King of the United States.

headline.print_headline: Duan Sets Up Jiangxi Open Final Against King
